IMMEDIATE
No.55/171784-Cab
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 31st October, 1984
9 Kartika, 1906(S).
The undersigned is directed to state that consequent on the
sad demise of Smt. Indira Gandhi, Prime Minister, the Council .of
Ministers stood dissolved with effect from
afternoon
of Wednesday,
October 31, 1984.
2.
The Members of the new Council of Ministers named in the
enclosed list assumed office with effect from the aftemoon of Wednesday,
October 31, 1984.
3.
The Ministry of Home Affairs may kindly take necessary action
regarding the issue of Gazette Notifications, etc.
(K! Ramfah)
Director.
To
The Ministry of Home Affairs,
(Shri S. Narayanaswamy Addl. Secretary),
New Delhi.
6871
the

CABINET SECRETARIA T
LIST OF MEMBERS OF THE CABINET
(As on 31-10-1984)
1, Shri Rajiv Gandhi
Prime Minister
2. Shri Pranab Kumar Mukherjee
3. Shri P.V, Narasimha Rao
4, Shri Shiv Shankar
5, Shri Buta Singh
